Package: HEMAscRaper
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Downloading and Analyzing HEMA Ratings Data
Version: 2.0.0
Author: Giuliano Giannetti
Maintainer: Giuliano Giannetti <giuliano@seznam.cz>
Description: Provides tools to download data from the HEMA Ratings website, including information on fighters, clubs, events, and tournament results. Includes functionality for calculating HEMA communities or "islands" using network graph analysis.
